    <item>
      <title>全球矿业领域的顶级交易</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/top-deals-global-mining-sector-2024-04-25/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团已出价 388 亿美元收购规模较小的竞争对手英美资源集团 (Anglo American)，提出一项打造全球最大铜矿商的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/top-deals-global-mining-sector-2024-04-25/</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 13:24:48 GMT</pubDate>
